{"claim_id": "claim_001", "text": "The goal of mspcompiler is to offer ways to compile either EI or tandem mass spectral libraries from various sources such as NIST, MoNA, and GPNS.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "The goal of mspcompiler is to offer ways to compile either EI or tandem\nmass spectral libraries from various sources, such as NIST (if you have\nit installed), MoNA, and GPNS, and organize them into a neat and\nup-to-date msp file that can be used in MS-DIAL.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_mspcompiler/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [132, 389], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": {"context": "mass spectrometry library compilation", "subject": "mspcompiler", "qualifier": "enables", "relation": "enables compilation of EI and tandem mass spectral libraries from multiple sources", "object": "organized msp files for MS-DIAL"}, "source_doi": null, "spine_entity_ids": ["SYS_MSPCOMPILER", "TOOL_MSDIAL"]}
{"claim_id": "claim_009", "text": "The RIKEN EI library already has SMILES and InChIKey well-organized, so no further treatment is needed.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "This file\nalready have SMILES and InChIKey well-organized. Hence, no further treatment is \nneeded.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_mspcompiler/synthesized_package", "source_section": "methods", "page": null, "char_span": [4658, 4756], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": null, "spine_entity_ids": ["DS_RIKEN_EI"]}
{"claim_id": "claim_011", "text": "The MoNA EI library file has SMILES information in the Comment field rather than the SMILES field.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "This file has SMILES information though, it is in\nthe *Comment* field.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_mspcompiler/synthesized_package", "source_section": "methods", "page": null, "char_span": [5095, 5165], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": null, "spine_entity_ids": ["DS_MONA_EI"]}
{"claim_id": "claim_012", "text": "The SMILES in MoNA EI library must be extracted from the Comment field and put into the SMILES field using the reorganize_mona function.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "Therefore, the SMILES has to be extracted from the *Comment*\nand put into the *SMILES* field by the *reorganize_mona* function.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_mspcompiler/synthesized_package", "source_section": "methods", "page": null, "char_span": [5166, 5293], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": null, "spine_entity_ids": ["TOOL_REORGANIZE_MONA", "DS_MONA_EI"]}
{"claim_id": "claim_021", "text": "Positive and negative modes in MS2 libraries are normally separated into 2 msp files.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "MS2 libraries can be processed in a similar way, but positive and negative modes\nare normally separated into 2 msp files.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_mspcompiler/synthesized_package", "source_section": "methods", "page": null, "char_span": [8081, 8202], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": null, "spine_entity_ids": []}
{"claim_id": "claim_023", "text": "The NIST MS2 exported msp file has both positive and negative modes mixed in a single file.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "2NIST* can be \nfound in \"C:/Programs/nist14/mssearch/nist_msms\". The exported msp file has both\npositive and negative modes mixed in a singled file", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_mspcompiler/synthesized_package", "source_section": "methods", "page": null, "char_span": [8370, 8517], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": null, "spine_entity_ids": ["DS_NIST_MS2"]}
{"claim_id": "claim_026", "text": "The GNPS library is organized in mgf format.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "Unlike others, the GNPS library is organized in mgf format", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_mspcompiler/synthesized_package", "source_section": "methods", "page": null, "char_span": [5085, 5144], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": null, "spine_entity_ids": ["COMP_MGF_FORMAT"]}
